You can sell your favorite NFTs directly on the Auctionity Saleroom by transferring them onto your account and creating your auctions on the Auctionity smart contract.

Sell NFTs

See an asset you like? Place bids on existing auctions using the ETH balance on your account.

Buy NFTs

Auctionity is all about the community: become an auctioneer, livestream auctions and you'll earn part of the final auction price!.

Host an auction

With Auctionity, auctions become viral thanks to the community. It allows everyone to earn money by promoting auctions on the platform.
